09:31.900 --> 09:33.860
It could keep itself going.

09:33.860 --> 09:35.380
It could grow.

09:35.380 --> 09:40.620
That moment set the slinky in motion and it's been going ever since.

09:40.620 --> 09:45.580
From the very first cells to you watching this now.

09:45.580 --> 09:50.260
